@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}
<div id="PostHeader"></div>
<body id="aboutBody">
    <h3 id="aboutHead">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
    <div id="freqQues" class="container">
        <br />

        <div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
            <div class="faqHeader">Food Donors</div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseOne">Is account registration required?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        Account registration at <strong>Marketplace for Humanity</strong> is only required if you will be creating a profile and posting to the Message Board.
                        This ensures a valid communication channel for all parties involved in any transactions.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwo">Will I get sued for donating?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        Please reference the link for the <span><a href="https://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/PLAW-104publ210/pdf/PLAW-104publ210.pdf" target="_blank">Good Samaritan</a></span> law.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThree">How do I know what to donate?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        Feel free to offer to donate any leftover, non-spoiled food your establishment has at the end of the day.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faqHeader">Charity</div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFour">Where do I find food donations?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseFour" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        When you login you should see the main posting area where food providers display what items are available at any particular time.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFive">How can I get food?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseFive" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        You have a few options:
                        <ul>
                            <li>Arrange to pick up donation</li>
                            <li>Arrange to have food provider drop off donation</li>
                            <li>Schedule through transportation providers</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseSix">How do we find food ingredients? Allergies? Dietary restrictions?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseSix" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        The food providers should list this in the main posting area but if you are unsure please feel free to ask them directly.
                        <br />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseSeven">What if I didn't receive my donation?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseSeven" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        Please contact the food provider and/or transportation provider as soon as possible. There may be a slight delay due to traffic or weather.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseEight">What is the rating system for?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseEight" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        The rating system conveys the quality of experience between charities, food providers and transport providers.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faqHeader">Transport Assistance</div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseNine">Do I get paid for this?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseNine" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        No, this would be considered a charitable donation of both your time and vehicle.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTen">How do I know pick-up/drop-off location and time?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseTen" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        This should be coordinated with the charity after they have confirmed with the food provider.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseEleven">What is the rating system for?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseEleven" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        The rating system conveys the quality of experience between charities, food providers and transport providers.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwelve">Can I deduct this on my taxes?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseTwelve" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        Answer <span><a href="https://www.irs.gov/credits-deductions/individuals/standard-mileage-rates-glance" target="_blank">HERE</a></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>